{
  "id": "adv_event_2207_01_01",
  "title": "アイドル\nミュージック\nフェス",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ⅢXが星見プロに移籍して間もない、ある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day‚ shortly after IIIX moved to Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "今月は仕事が一件もないってどういうこと！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean there's no work for this month!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9666666667,
      "endTime": 6.4561677138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、営業をかけてはいるんですが\nなかなか難しくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ I've been making sales calls‚\nbut it's quite difficult…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6666666667,
      "endTime": 11.504898039499999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "プレタポルテの不祥事でスリクスの評判が\n地に落ちたのは分かっています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that IIIX's reputation plummeted\ndue to the Pret-A-Porter scandal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7,
      "endTime": 16.6586623192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "おかげで仕事も干されてしまって\nI-UNITY以降、私達は\nまともに活動出来ていません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to that‚ we've been deprived of work as well.\nSince I-UNITY‚ we haven't been\nable to actively engage in activities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9333333333,
      "endTime": 23.8107728193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "このままフリーで活動していても目的には遠い……\nそう思ったから私達は提案を受けたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we continue to work as freelancers‚ we won't achieve our goals…\nThat's why we accepted the proposal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1666666667,
      "endTime": 31.649100594300002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "それなのにこっちでも仕事がないんじゃ\n星見プロに入った意味ないじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yet‚ if there's no work here either‚\nthen joining Hoshimi Pro was pointless‚ wasn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.9,
      "endTime": 37.2671678143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "仕事の一つも取って来れないなんて\nマネージャーの才能ないんじゃないですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not being able to secure any work…\nMaybe the manager lacks talent‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4666666667,
      "endTime": 43.3098456322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "これなら姫野の方がマシだったかも\nあいつ、性格は悪いけど仕事は有能だったからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ Himeno might have been better.\nShe had a bad personality‚ but she was competent in her work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6,
      "endTime": 51.2442092394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "kana、さすがにそれは言い過ぎよ\nごめんなさい。この子、口が悪くて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kana‚ that's going too far.\nI'm sorry. She has a sharp tongue…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7,
      "endTime": 57.8459046681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "あー、何一人だけいい子ぶってるの！？\n武田さんってそういうとこあるよねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ why are you pretending to be the only good one!?\nTakeda-san‚ you're always that way‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0666666667,
      "endTime": 63.871428571399996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくmihoがかばってくれてるのに\nあんたって恩知らずね。少しは感謝したら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though Miho is defending you‚\nyou're ungrateful. Shouldn't you show a little gratitude?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.1333333333,
      "endTime": 70.8068143111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～？　誰もかばってほしいなんて言ってませ～ん\n恩着せがましくしないで下さ～い",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? I never said I wanted anyone to defend me.\nDon't you dare act so high and mighty.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71,
      "endTime": 78.343118758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "二人ともやめなさい\nそんなことより今は仕事の話でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of you‚ stop it.\nNow‚ let's talk about work now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5666666667,
      "endTime": 83.0127546184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるわよ。私達はこんな所で終わる訳には\nいかない……私にはお金が必要なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. We can't end it here…\nI need money‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.3666666667,
      "endTime": 91.9971711104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "お金お金って、山田さんはそればっかりだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Money money bla bla bla‚Yamada-san. That's all you care about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.4,
      "endTime": 97.12947864530001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "SNSのいいねの数ばかり気にしてるあなたに\n言われたくないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to hear that from someone\nwho only cares about the number of likes on SNS.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.3333333333,
      "endTime": 101.5905997178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "はあ？　何それ、喧嘩売ってるんですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Are you picking a fight with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8,
      "endTime": 106.0658050537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "二人ともやめなさい……でも{user}さん\nこのまま終わる気がないのは全員同じ気持ちです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both of you‚ stop it… But {user}-san‚\nNone of us have the intention to end it like this. If we can stand on stage‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.2666666667,
      "endTime": 114.05798922970001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "ステージにさえ立てれば必ず返り咲いてみせます\nⅢXにはそれだけの実力がありますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "we will definitely make a comeback.\nWe have the skills for ⅢX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4666666667,
      "endTime": 121.13092171349999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "そーゆーことだから\n早く大きな仕事取って来て下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why…\nGo get a real work for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3333333333,
      "endTime": 125.8754194132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "今日はそれだけ言いに来ました\nそれじゃ、連絡待ってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's all I came here to say today.\nI'll be waiting for your update.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.1333333333,
      "endTime": 131.3058874534,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5666.66666670001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5766.6666667000045
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6033.333333399994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "やれやれ……\nまあ、この状況じゃ文句の一つも言いたくなるよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew…\nWell‚ I can understand why they want to complain in this situation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.4,
      "endTime": 140.29842938750002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスの実力と実績は申し分ないし、三枝さんが\n言っていたあの話、ダメ元で掛け合ってみるか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IIIX's abilities and track record. Should I just\ntell them what Saegusa-san offtered…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.4666666667,
      "endTime": 148.083401378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.8,
      "endTime": 150.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　スリクスがアイドルミュージックフェスに\n出演するんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? IIIX is going to perform\nat the Idol Music Festival!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.0666666667,
      "endTime": 156.56567296789999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "IMFって確か日本最大級の\n野外アイドルフェスですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "IMF is one of the biggest\noutdoor idol festivals in Japan‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.7666666667,
      "endTime": 161.847689678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2207_01_01-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "そこにkana達をねじ込むなんてやるじゃない\nただのお人好しの凡マネージャーじゃなかったんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice job of putting kana and the others in that tho.\nYou're not just an ordinary kind-hearted manager‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.0666666667,
      "endTime": 169.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
